                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I hadn't solo'd or duo'd in HoH in ages, been bored lately and went back to hammer out some AAs pre OoW.
<br />

<br />
The shrines are great, but I find they are usually camped and frankly don't have enough mobs.
<br />

<br />
My preferred spot - Wrulon alley (hang a right at ZI, hang a right at T - you're there).
<br />

<br />
Along this path you've got 6 Wrulons, 7 Black Armors, 7 guards and 3 higher level roamers - 23 mobs....
<br />

<br />
Tash and Charm a Wrulons, NDT and Haste it, hand it some mage gear (neck, belt, weapons).
<br />

<br />
Then go to town pulling everything you can as quickly as possible - tash, slow, asphyxiate.
<br />

<br />
While the pet is killing one mob I'm usually pulling the next closest.  Every now and then I throw in a nuke to use up some surplus mana.
<br />

<br />
When the pet gets too low on health to take on another mob, recant it, kill it and grab another one.
<br />

<br />
May not get max exp per mob but I can usually get through 20-23 mobs before I get repop.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91734" target="_blank" class="postlink">Brackus/</a><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=84239" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"> Aramus /</span></a><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=461299" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Coball</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
